#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:16
msgid "Stone"
msgstr "石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:17
msgid ""
"One of the most common blocks in the world, almost the entire underground "
"consists of stone. It sometimes contains ores. Stone may be created when "
"water meets lava."
msgstr ""
"世界で最も一般的なブロックの一つで、地下のほぼ全体が石で構成されています。時"
"には鉱石を含むこともあります。水と溶岩が出会って石ができる場合もあります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:31
msgid "Coal Ore"
msgstr "石炭鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:32
msgid ""
"Some coal contained in stone, it is very common and can be found inside "
"stone in medium to large clusters at nearly every height."
msgstr ""
"石に含まれる石炭はとても一般的で、ほぼすべての高さにおいて、中～大規模なまと"
"まりで見つけることができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:45
msgid "Iron Ore"
msgstr "鉄鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:46
msgid ""
"Some iron contained in stone, it is prety common and can be found below sea "
"level."
msgstr "石に含まれる鉄はかなり一般的で、海面下の高さで見つけられます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:59
msgid "Gold Ore"
msgstr "金鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:60
msgid "This stone contains pure gold, a rare metal."
msgstr "この石には、希少金属である純金が含まれています。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:83
msgid "Redstone Ore"
msgstr "レッドストーン鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:84
msgid ""
"Redstone ore is commonly found near the bottom of the world. It glows when "
"it is punched or walked upon."
msgstr ""
"レッドストーン鉱石は、ワールドの低層に多く見られます。それをパンチしたり、踏"
"んだりすると光ります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:118
msgid "Lit Redstone Ore"
msgstr "発光したレッドストーン鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:152
msgid "Lapis Lazuli Ore"
msgstr "ラピスラズリ鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:153
msgid ""
"Lapis lazuli ore is the ore of lapis lazuli. It can be rarely found in "
"clusters near the bottom of the world."
msgstr ""
"ラピスラズリ鉱石は、ワールドの深層あたりで群生しているのが稀に見つかります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:175
msgid "Emerald Ore"
msgstr "エメラルド鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:176
msgid ""
"Emerald ore is the ore of emeralds. It is very rare and can be found alone, "
"not in clusters."
msgstr "エメラルド鉱石は非常に希少で、群生しておらず、単独で見つけられます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:188
msgid "Diamond Ore"
msgstr "ダイヤモンド鉱石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:189
msgid ""
"Diamond ore is rare and can be found in clusters near the bottom of the "
"world."
msgstr "ダイヤモンド鉱石は希少で、ワールドの深層近くでまとまって見つかります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:201
msgid "Stone Bricks"
msgstr "石レンガ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:214
msgid "Chiseled Stone Bricks"
msgstr "模様入り石レンガ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:226
msgid "Cracked Stone Bricks"
msgstr "ひび割れた石レンガ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:237
msgid "Mossy Stone Bricks"
msgstr "苔むした石レンガ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:248
msgid "Smooth Stone"
msgstr "滑らかな石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:259
msgid "Granite"
msgstr "花崗岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:260
msgid "Granite is an igneous rock."
msgstr "花崗岩とは、火成岩の一種です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:270
msgid "Polished Granite"
msgstr "磨かれた花崗岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:271
msgid "Polished granite is a decorative building block made from granite."
msgstr "磨かれた花崗岩は装飾的な建築用ブロックで、花崗岩から作られます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:282
msgid "Andesite"
msgstr "安山岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:283
msgid "Andesite is an igneous rock."
msgstr "安山岩とは、火成岩の一種です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:293
msgid "Polished Andesite"
msgstr "磨かれた安山岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:294
msgid "Polished andesite is a decorative building block made from andesite."
msgstr "磨かれた安山岩は装飾的な建築用ブロックで、安山岩から作られます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:305
msgid "Diorite"
msgstr "閃緑岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:306
msgid "Diorite is an igneous rock."
msgstr "閃緑岩とは、火成岩の一種です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:316
msgid "Polished Diorite"
msgstr "磨かれた閃緑岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:317
msgid "Polished diorite is a decorative building block made from diorite."
msgstr "磨かれた閃緑岩は装飾的な建築用ブロックで、閃緑岩から作られます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:329
msgid "Grass Block"
msgstr "草原"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:330
msgid ""
"A grass block is dirt with a grass cover. Grass blocks are resourceful "
"blocks which allow the growth of all sorts of plants. They can be turned "
"into farmland with a hoe and turned into grass paths with a shovel. In "
"light, the grass slowly spreads onto dirt nearby. Under an opaque block or a "
"liquid, a grass block may turn back to dirt."
msgstr ""
"草原とは、土に草を被せたものです。草原は、さまざまな植物を育てることができ"
"る、資源的なブロックです。クワで農地にしたり、シャベルでオフロードにしたりで"
"きます。光に当たると、近くの土の上に草がゆっくりと広がっていきます。不透明な"
"ブロックや液体の下では、草原は土に戻ることがあります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:368
msgid "Dirt with Snow"
msgstr "雪が積もった土"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:372
msgid "Grass Path"
msgstr "オフロード"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:373
msgid ""
"Grass paths are a decorative variant of grass blocks. Their top has a "
"different color and they are a bit lower than grass blocks, making them "
"useful to build footpaths. Grass paths can be created with a shovel. A grass "
"path turns into dirt when it is below a solid block."
msgstr ""
"オフロードは、草原の装飾的なバリエーションです。上部の色が異なり、草原より少"
"し低いので、道にうってつけです。シャベルで作れます。オフロードは、固いブロッ"
"クの下にあると土になります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:392
msgid "Mycelium"
msgstr "菌糸"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:393
msgid ""
"Mycelium is a type of dirt and the ideal soil for mushrooms. Unlike other "
"dirt-type blocks, it can not be turned into farmland with a hoe. In light, "
"mycelium slowly spreads over nearby dirt. Under an opaque block or a liquid, "
"it eventually turns back into dirt."
msgstr ""
"菌糸は土の一種であり、キノコに最適な土壌です。他の土系ブロックと違い、クワで"
"農地に変えられません。光に当たると、菌糸は近くの土の上にゆっくりと広がってい"
"きます。不透明なブロックや液体の下では、それはやがて土に戻ります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:407
msgid "Mycelium with Snow"
msgstr "雪が積もった菌糸"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:454
msgid "Podzol"
msgstr "ポドゾル"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:455
msgid ""
"Podzol is a type of dirt found in taiga forests. Only a few plants are able "
"to survive on it."
msgstr ""
"ポドゾルとは、タイガの森で見つかる土の一種です。その上で生きられる植物はごく"
"わずかです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:466
msgid "Podzol with Snow"
msgstr "雪が積もったポドゾル"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:469
msgid "Dirt"
msgstr "土"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:470
msgid ""
"Dirt acts as a soil for a few plants. When in light, this block may grow a "
"grass or mycelium cover if such blocks are nearby."
msgstr ""
"土はいくつかの植物のための土壌として機能します。明るいところで近くに草や菌糸"
"で覆われたブロックがあれば、このブロックの表層にもそれら成長させることがあり"
"ます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:481
msgid "Coarse Dirt"
msgstr "粗い土"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:482
msgid ""
"Coarse dirt acts as a soil for some plants and is similar to dirt, but it "
"will never grow a cover."
msgstr ""
"粗い土は、一部の植物の土として機能し、土と類似してはいますが、表層を何かが覆"
"うことがありません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:492
msgid "Gravel"
msgstr "砂利"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:493
msgid ""
"This block consists of a couple of loose stones and can't support itself."
msgstr ""
"このブロックは緩い石の組み合わせで構成されており、自身を支えられません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:527
msgid "Sand"
msgstr "砂"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:528
msgid "Sand is found in large quantities at beaches and deserts."
msgstr "砂は、海岸や砂漠で大量に見つかります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:539
msgid "Sandstone"
msgstr "砂岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:541
msgid "Sandstone is compressed sand and is a rather soft kind of stone."
msgstr "砂岩は砂を圧縮したもので、やや軟らかい種類の石です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:551
msgid "Cut Sandstone"
msgstr "溝入り砂岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:552
