msgstr "模様入り砂岩は、装飾用ブロックです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:573
msgid "Smooth Sandstone"
msgstr "滑らかな砂岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:575
msgid "Smooth sandstone is compressed sand and is a rather soft kind of stone."
msgstr "滑らかな砂岩は、装飾的な建築ブロックです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:588
msgid "Red Sand"
msgstr "赤い砂"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:589
msgid "Red sand is found in large quantities in mesa biomes."
msgstr "赤い砂は、メサバイオームで大量に見つかります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:599
msgid "Red Sandstone"
msgstr "赤い砂岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:600
msgid ""
"Red sandstone is compressed red sand and is a rather soft kind of stone."
msgstr "赤い砂岩は赤い砂を圧縮したもので、やや軟らかい種類の石です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:610
msgid "Cut Red Sandstone"
msgstr "溝入り赤い砂岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:611
msgid "Cut red sandstone is a decorative building block."
msgstr "溝入り赤い砂岩は、装飾用ブロックです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:621
msgid "Chiseled Red Sandstone"
msgstr "模様入り赤い砂岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:622
msgid "Chiseled red sandstone is a decorative building block."
msgstr "模様入り赤い砂岩は、装飾用ブロックです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:632
msgid "Smooth Red Sandstone"
msgstr "滑らかな赤い砂岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:633
msgid "Smooth red sandstone is a decorative building block."
msgstr "滑らかな赤い砂岩は、装飾的な建築ブロックです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:645
msgid "Clay"
msgstr "粘土"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:646
msgid "Clay is a versatile kind of earth commonly found at beaches underwater."
msgstr "粘土は海水浴中によく見つかる、汎用性の高い土の一種です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:659
msgid "Brick Block"
msgstr "レンガブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:660
msgid ""
"Brick blocks are a good building material for building solid houses and can "
"take quite a punch."
msgstr ""
"レンガブロックは、頑丈な家を建てるのに適した建材で、かなりの衝撃にも耐えられ"
"ます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:671
msgid "Bedrock"
msgstr "岩盤"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:672
msgid ""
"Bedrock is a very hard type of rock. It can not be broken, destroyed, "
"collected or moved by normal means, unless in Creative Mode."
msgstr ""
"岩盤は非常に硬い岩石の一種です。（クリエイティブモードでない限り）通常の手段"
"では壊したり、破壊したり、集めたり、移動させることはできません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:673
msgid ""
"In the End dimension, starting a fire on this block will create an eternal "
"fire."
msgstr ""
"エンドの次元では、このブロック上で火を起こすと、永続的な炎が生まれます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:715
msgid "Cobblestone"
msgstr "丸石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:728
msgid "Mossy Cobblestone"
msgstr "苔むした丸石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:739
msgid "Block of Coal"
msgstr "石炭ブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:740
msgid ""
"Blocks of coal are useful as a compact storage of coal and very useful as a "
"furnace fuel. A block of coal is as efficient as 10 coal."
msgstr ""
"石炭ブロックは、石炭をコンパクトに保管でき、炉の燃料として非常に便利です。1個"
"の石炭ブロックは、10個の石炭と同じ効率です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:752
msgid "Block of Iron"
msgstr "鉄ブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:753
msgid ""
"A block of iron is mostly a decorative block but also useful as a compact "
"storage of iron ingots."
msgstr ""
"鉄ブロックは、主に装飾用のブロックですが、鉄インゴットをコンパクトに保管する"
"のにも便利です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:764
msgid "Block of Gold"
msgstr "金ブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:765
msgid ""
"A block of gold is mostly a shiny decorative block but also useful as a "
"compact storage of gold ingots."
msgstr ""
"金ブロックは、主に装飾用の輝くブロックですが、金インゴットをコンパクトに保管"
"するのにも便利です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:776
msgid "Block of Diamond"
msgstr "ダイヤモンドブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:777
msgid ""
"A block of diamond is mostly a shiny decorative block but also useful as a "
"compact storage of diamonds."
msgstr ""
"ダイヤモンドブロックは、主に装飾用の輝くブロックですが、ダイヤモンドをコンパ"
"クトに保管するのにも便利です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:788
msgid "Block of Lapis Lazuli"
msgstr "ラピスラズリブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:789
msgid ""
"A lapis lazuli block is mostly a decorative block but also useful as a "
"compact storage of lapis lazuli."
msgstr ""
"ラピスラズリブロックは、主に装飾用のブロックですが、ラピスラズリをコンパクト"
"に保管するのにも便利です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:799
msgid "Block of Emerald"
msgstr "エメラルドブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:800
msgid ""
"A block of emerald is mostly a shiny decorative block but also useful as a "
"compact storage of emeralds."
msgstr ""
"エメラルドブロックは、主に装飾用の輝くブロックですが、エメラルドをコンパクト"
"に保管するのにも便利です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:811
msgid "Obsidian"
msgstr "黒曜石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:812
msgid ""
"Obsidian is an extremely hard mineral with an enourmous blast-resistance. "
"Obsidian is formed when water meets lava."
msgstr ""
"黒曜石は、とてつもなく硬い鉱物で耐爆性が抜群です。黒曜石は、水と溶岩が出会っ"
"て形成されたものです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:822
msgid "Crying Obsidian"
msgstr "泣く黒曜石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:823
msgid ""
"Crying obsidian is a luminous obsidian that can generate as part of ruined "
"portals."
msgstr ""
"泣く黒曜石は、廃墟のポータルの一部として生成可能な、発光する黒曜石です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:834
msgid "Ice"
msgstr "氷"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:835
msgid ""
"Ice is a solid block usually found in cold areas. It melts near block light "
"sources at a light level of 12 or higher. When it melts or is broken while "
"resting on top of another block, it will turn into a water source."
msgstr ""
"氷は、通常寒い地域にある固体ブロックです。明るさ12以上の光源ブロック付近では"
"溶けます。他のブロックの上に乗っているときに溶けたり割れたりすると、水源に変"
"わります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:853
msgid "Packed Ice"
msgstr "氷塊"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:854
msgid "Packed ice is a compressed form of ice. It is opaque and solid."
msgstr "氷塊は、氷が圧縮した形態です。不透明で固形です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:869
msgid "Blue Ice"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:870
msgid ""
"Blue Ice is a still more compressed form of ice.  It is opaque and solid."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:913
msgid ""
"Frosted ice is a short-lived solid block. It melts into a water source "
"within a few seconds."
msgstr "薄氷は短命の固形ブロックです。水源の中では数秒で融けてしまいます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:916
msgid "Frosted Ice"
msgstr "薄氷"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:1011
msgid "Top Snow"
msgstr "積雪"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:1012
msgid "Stackable"
msgstr "スタック可能"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:1013
msgid ""
"Top snow is a layer of snow. It melts near light sources other than the sun "
"with a light level of 12 or higher."
msgstr "積雪とは、雪の層です。太陽を除く明るさ12以上の光源付近で融けます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:1013
msgid ""
"Top snow can be stacked and has one of 8 different height levels. At levels "
"2-8, top snow is collidable. Top snow drops 2-9 snowballs, depending on its "
"height."
msgstr ""
"積雪は積み重ねることができ、8段階の高さが選べます。2～8段では、積雪に衝突性が"
"あります。積雪は高さに応じて2～9個の雪玉を落とします。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:1014
msgid ""
"This block can only be placed on full solid blocks and on another top snow "
"(which increases its height)."
msgstr ""
"このブロックは、完全な固体ブロックの上と、別の積雪の上にしか置けません（高さ"
"が増えます）。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:1065
msgid "Snow"
msgstr "雪"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_base.lua:1066
msgid ""
"This is a full block of snow. Snow of this thickness is usually found in "
"areas of extreme cold."
msgstr ""
"これは１ブロックサイズの雪です。この厚さの雪は、おおむね極寒の地で見られま"
"す。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:6
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:54
msgid "Cactus"
msgstr "サボテン"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:7
msgid "Grows on sand"
msgstr "砂の上に生育"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:7
msgid "Contact damage: @1 per half second"
msgstr "接触ダメージ：@1/0.5秒"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:8
msgid ""
"This is a piece of cactus commonly found in dry areas, especially deserts. "
"Over time, cacti will grow up to 3 blocks high on sand or red sand. A cactus "
"hurts living beings touching it with a damage of 1 HP every half second. "
"When a cactus block is broken, all cactus blocks connected above it will "
"break as well."
msgstr ""
"これは乾燥した地域、特に砂漠によく見られるサボテンの一種です。サボテンは砂や"
"赤い砂の上で時間が経つと、3ブロックの高さまで成長します。サボテンはそれに触れ"
"た生物を傷つけます（1HP/0.5秒のダメージ）。サボテンのブロックが壊れると、その"
"上につながっているすべてのサボテンのブロックも壊れます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:9
msgid "A cactus can only be placed on top of another cactus or any sand."
msgstr "サボテンは、他のサボテンや砂の上にしか置けません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:77
msgid "Cactus Flower"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:78
msgid "Grows on cacti"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:100
msgid "Sugar Canes"
msgstr "サトウキビ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:101
msgid "Grows on sand or dirt next to water"
msgstr "水辺の砂や土の上に生育"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:102
msgid ""
"Sugar canes are a plant which has some uses in crafting. Sugar canes will "
"slowly grow up to 3 blocks when they are next to water and are placed on a "
"grass block, dirt, sand, red sand, podzol or coarse dirt. When a sugar cane "
"is broken, all sugar canes connected above will break as well."
msgstr ""
"サトウキビはクラフトに使える植物です。水のある場所で、草原、土、砂、赤い砂、"
"ポドゾル、粗い土の上にサトウキビを置くと、ゆっくりと3ブロックまで成長します。"
"サトウキビが折れるときは、上につながっているすべてのサトウキビも折れます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_cactuscane.lua:103
msgid ""
"Sugar canes can only be placed top of other sugar canes and on top of blocks "
"on which they would grow."
msgstr ""
"サトウキビは、他のサトウキビの上や、サトウキビが成長するブロックの上にしか置"
"けません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_climb.lua:15
msgid "Ladder"
msgstr "ハシゴ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_climb.lua:16
msgid ""
"A piece of ladder which allows you to climb vertically. Ladders can only be "
"placed on the side of solid blocks and not on glass, leaves, ice, slabs, "
"glowstone, nor sea lanterns."
msgstr ""
"垂直によじ登ることができるハシゴの一部です。ハシゴは固いブロックの側面にのみ"
"設置でき、ガラス、葉、氷、スラブ、グローストーン、シーランタンの上には設置で"
"きません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_climb.lua:83
msgid "Vines"
msgstr "ツタ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_climb.lua:84
msgid ""
"Vines are climbable blocks which can be placed on the sides of solid full-"
"cube blocks. Vines slowly grow and spread."
msgstr ""
"ツタは、フルサイズのブロックの側面に配置できる、よじ登り可能なブロックです。"
"ツタはゆっくりと成長し、広がっていきます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_glass.lua:6
msgid "Glass"
msgstr "ガラス"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_glass.lua:7
msgid "A decorative and mostly transparent block."
msgstr "装飾用の、ほとんどが透明なブロックです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_glass.lua:33
msgid ""
"Stained glass is a decorative and mostly transparent block which comes in "
"various different colors."
msgstr ""
"色ガラスは、そのほとんどが透明な装飾ブロックで、さまざまなカラーバリエーショ"
"ンがあります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_glass.lua:34
msgid "Stained Glass"
msgstr "色ガラス"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_glow_lichen.lua:60
msgid "Glow Lichen"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_glow_lichen.lua:61
msgid ""
"Naturally generating non-solid block that emits a faint light and can attach "
"to any surface of a solid block."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:11
msgid "Flowing Water"
msgstr "流れる水"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:55
msgid "Water Source"
msgstr "水源"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:56
msgid "Water"
msgstr "水"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:58
msgid ""
"Water is abundant in oceans and also appears in a few springs in the ground. "
"You can swim easily in water, but you need to catch your breath from time to "
"time."
msgstr ""
"水は海に豊富にあり、また地中のわずかな湧水にも現れます。水中では簡単に泳ぐこ"
"とができますが、時々息を整える必要があります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:59
msgid "Water interacts with lava in various ways:"
msgstr "水は溶岩とさまざまな形で相互作用します："

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:60
msgid ""
"• When water is directly above or horizontally next to a lava source, the "
"lava turns into obsidian."
msgstr "・溶岩源の上や横に水が隣接すると、溶岩源は黒曜石に変化します。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:61
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:165
msgid ""
"• When flowing water touches flowing lava either from above or horizontally, "
"the lava turns into cobblestone."
msgstr "・流れる溶岩の上や横に流れる水が触れると、溶岩は丸石に変化します。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:62
msgid "• When water is directly below lava, the water turns into stone."
msgstr "・水が溶岩の真下にあると、水は石に変化します。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:103
msgid "Flowing Lava"
msgstr "流れる溶岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:152
msgid ""
"A lava source sets fire to a couple of air blocks above when they're next to "
"a flammable block."
msgstr ""
"溶岩源は、可燃性ブロックの隣にあると、その上の空気ブロック数個に火をつけま"
"す。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:158
msgid "Lava Source"
msgstr "溶岩源"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:161
msgid ""
"Lava is hot and rather dangerous. Don't touch it, it will hurt you a lot and "
"it is hard to get out."
msgstr ""
"溶岩は熱くてだいぶ危険です。触れてはいけません、とても痛いし、出るのも大変で"
"す。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:163
msgid "Lava interacts with water various ways:"
msgstr "溶岩は水とさまざまな相互作用をします："

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:164
msgid ""
"• When a lava source is directly below or horizontally next to water, the "
"lava turns into obsidian."
msgstr "・溶岩源が水の下や横に隣接している場合、溶岩源は黒曜石に変化します。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_liquid.lua:166
msgid "• When lava is directly above water, the water turns into stone."
msgstr "・溶岩が水の真上にあると、水は石に変化します。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:5
msgid "Bone Block"
msgstr "骨ブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:6
msgid "Bone blocks are decorative blocks and a compact storage of bone meal."
msgstr "骨ブロックは装飾用ブロックで、骨粉をコンパクトに保管できます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:19
msgid "Slime Block"
msgstr "スライムブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:20
msgid "Slime blocks are very bouncy and prevent fall damage."
msgstr ""
"スライムブロックは非常に弾力性があり、落下ダメージを防ぐことができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:53
msgid "Cobweb"
msgstr "クモの巣"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:54
msgid "Slows down movement"
msgstr "動きが遅くなる"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:55
msgid "Cobwebs can be walked through, but significantly slow you down."
msgstr "クモの巣は歩いて通過できますが、大幅にノロくなります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:74 mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:113
msgid "Dead Bush"
msgstr "枯れ木"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:75
msgid ""
"Dead bushes are unremarkable plants often found in dry areas. They can be "
"harvested for sticks."
msgstr ""
"枯れ木は、乾燥した場所によく見られる、路傍の植物です。棒として採取できます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:122
msgid "Barrier"
msgstr "バリア"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:123
msgid ""
"Barriers are invisible walkable blocks. They are used to create boundaries "
"of adventure maps and the like. Monsters and animals won't appear on "
"barriers, and fences do not connect to barriers. Other blocks can be built "
"on barriers like on any other block."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:124
msgid ""
"When you hold a barrier in hand, you reveal all placed barriers in a short "
"distance around you."
msgstr ""
"バリアを手にすると、周囲の近距離に配置されたバリアがすべて表示されます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:176
msgid "Realm Barrier"
msgstr "領域障壁"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:209
msgid "Light"
msgstr "光"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:210
msgid ""
"Lights are invisible blocks. They are used to light up adventure maps and "
"the like."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:211
msgid ""
"When you hold a light in hand, you reveal all placed lights in a short "
"distance around you."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_misc.lua:263
msgid "Void"
msgstr "奈落"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:5
msgid "Stone Stairs"
msgstr "石の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:6
msgid "Stone Slab"
msgstr "石のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:12
msgid "Smooth Stone Slab"
msgstr "滑らかな石のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:19
msgid "Andesite Stairs"
msgstr "安山岩の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:20
msgid "Andesite Slab"
msgstr "安山岩のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:25
msgid "Granite Stairs"
msgstr "花崗岩の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:26
msgid "Granite Slab"
msgstr "花崗岩のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:31
msgid "Diorite Stairs"
msgstr "閃緑岩の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:32
msgid "Diorite Slab"
msgstr "閃緑岩のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:38
msgid "Cobblestone Stairs"
msgstr "丸石の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:39
msgid "Cobblestone Slab"
msgstr "丸石のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:44
msgid "Mossy Cobblestone Stairs"
msgstr "苔むした丸石の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:45
msgid "Mossy Cobblestone Slab"
msgstr "苔むした丸石のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:51
msgid "Brick Stairs"
msgstr "レンガの階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:52
msgid "Brick Slab"
msgstr "レンガのハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:59
msgid "Sandstone Stairs"
msgstr "砂岩の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:60
msgid "Sandstone Slab"
msgstr "砂岩のハーフブロック"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:65
msgid "Smooth Sandstone Stairs"
msgstr "滑らかな砂岩の階段"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_core/nodes_stairs.lua:66
msgid "Smooth Sandstone Slab"
msgstr "滑らかな砂岩のハーフブロック"

